HEADWORD: Trippingly
<hw>Trip"ping*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a tripping manner; with a
light, nimble, quick step; with agility; nimbly.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Sing, and dance it <qex>trippingly</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Speak the speech . . . <qex>trippingly</qex> on the tongue.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tripsis</ent>⟦br⟧
